{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-tsx","path":"/2018-10-24-css-drawing-tutorial/","webpackCompilationHash":"69b55ce51e98823e248b","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Kyoungah's dev blog.","author":"Kyoungah"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7fcf786a-e6de-56f6-8a78-9c37f1e53afa","excerpt":"요즘 css drawing 에 맛들려 시간날 때마다 조금씩 css drawing을 작업하다가 튜토리얼을 간단하게 작성해보기로 했다. \n위의 이미지는 호무새 방송시 구독 메시지와 같이 출력되는 이미지인데 튜토리얼용으로도 괜찮을것 같아서 캡쳐해왔다. css…","html":"<p>요즘 css drawing 에 맛들려 시간날 때마다 조금씩 css drawing을 작업하다가 튜토리얼을 간단하게 작성해보기로 했다.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 95.45454545454545%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"출처: 치킨쿤 유튜브 썸네일\"\n        title=\"출처: 치킨쿤 유튜브 썸네일\"\n        src=\"/static/28a4093b7748f5beb3961f82813a9592/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/28a4093b7748f5beb3961f82813a9592/cf440/css-drawing-tutorial-01.png 148w,\n/static/28a4093b7748f5beb3961f82813a9592/d2d38/css-drawing-tutorial-01.png 295w,\n/static/28a4093b7748f5beb3961f82813a9592/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-01.png 590w,\n/static/28a4093b7748f5beb3961f82813a9592/ad9ce/css-drawing-tutorial-01.png 704w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">출처: 치킨쿤 유튜브 썸네일</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n위의 이미지는 호무새 방송시 구독 메시지와 같이 출력되는 이미지인데 튜토리얼용으로도 괜찮을것 같아서 캡쳐해왔다. css로 이 이미지를 한번 작업해보자.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 95.97701149425288%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"css drawing tutorial 02\"\n        title=\"css drawing tutorial 02\"\n        src=\"/static/40fdeb21e57721a6a693d0fc37d455e6/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/40fdeb21e57721a6a693d0fc37d455e6/cf440/css-drawing-tutorial-02.png 148w,\n/static/40fdeb21e57721a6a693d0fc37d455e6/d2d38/css-drawing-tutorial-02.png 295w,\n/static/40fdeb21e57721a6a693d0fc37d455e6/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-02.png 590w,\n/static/40fdeb21e57721a6a693d0fc37d455e6/a82ee/css-drawing-tutorial-02.png 696w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n먼저 어떻게 영역을 나눠볼지 정해보자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>호무새<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>./angry-heavy-rain.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>heavy-rain<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>heavy-rain-eyes left<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>heavy-rain-eyes right<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>heavy-rain-mouse-line<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>heavy-rain-mouse<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>얼굴안에 눈, 부리가 있으니 얼굴이 될 div안에 눈, 부리 영역을 div로 잡아 넣어주었다. 이제 css를 작성해보자.</p>\n<h2>얼굴</h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 104.16666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"호무새 얼굴\"\n        title=\"호무새 얼굴\"\n        src=\"/static/d9a16dbeadb816cfe2cabb7d81b44e1a/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d9a16dbeadb816cfe2cabb7d81b44e1a/cf440/css-drawing-tutorial-03.png 148w,\n/static/d9a16dbeadb816cfe2cabb7d81b44e1a/d2d38/css-drawing-tutorial-03.png 295w,\n/static/d9a16dbeadb816cfe2cabb7d81b44e1a/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-03.png 590w,\n/static/d9a16dbeadb816cfe2cabb7d81b44e1a/331ea/css-drawing-tutorial-03.png 864w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">호무새 얼굴</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 얼굴 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 380px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 380px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px auto 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #54bc89<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 머리 위의 꽁지들 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain:before,\n.heavy-rain:after</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50% 50% 50% 50% / 40% 40% 60% 60%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #54bc89<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain:before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 90px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>20deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain:after</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 65px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>45deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>div 하나를 호무새 얼굴로 잡고 가상 선택자(before, after)로 호무새의 꽁지를 표현했다.\n가상 선택자는 존재하지 않는 요소를 존재하는 것처럼 부여하여 문서의 특정 부분 선택이 가능하다.</p>\n<h2>호무새 눈</h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 109.83213429256595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"호무새 눈\"\n        title=\"호무새 눈\"\n        src=\"/static/b04cefbc4daaa1d0337b037dc3023d19/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b04cefbc4daaa1d0337b037dc3023d19/cf440/css-drawing-tutorial-04.png 148w,\n/static/b04cefbc4daaa1d0337b037dc3023d19/d2d38/css-drawing-tutorial-04.png 295w,\n/static/b04cefbc4daaa1d0337b037dc3023d19/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-04.png 590w,\n/static/b04cefbc4daaa1d0337b037dc3023d19/1d25d/css-drawing-tutorial-04.png 834w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">호무새 눈</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 눈 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffffff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px solid #000000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 120px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes.left</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes.right</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes:before,\n.heavy-rain-eyes:after</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 눈썹 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes:before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 35px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -15px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes.left:before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>20deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes.right:before</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-20deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 눈동자 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.heavy-rain-eyes:after</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffffff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px 10px 0px 13px #000000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>역시 가상선택자로 눈알을 표현했다. before는 눈썹, after로는 그림자를 사용하여 눈동자를 나타내었다.</p>\n<h2>호무새 부리</h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 105.03432494279177%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"호무새 부리\"\n        title=\"호무새 부리\"\n        src=\"/static/29f284fa67868c49c4e982d2a8f6eec5/b9e4f/css-drawing-tutorial-05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/29f284fa67868c4